metadata.name: U.V. Portal
metadata.description:
Portals is a series inspired by movement, perception and fragmentation. How art helps me navigate the world. How my arts perceived when I share It and what can be found in the fragments.

" U.V. Portal" is a continuation of the portals series. This piece came out of curiosity and experimentation in procreate. pushing into the color spectrum and playing with ideas around moods, different types of people, and things beyond visible light. "
